  """
  New start date in YYYY-MM-DD format; must be within 1 year in the past and 20 years in the future
  """
  start: String
  """
  New end date in YYYY-MM-DD format; must be within 1 year in the past and 20 years in the future
  """
  end: String
}

"""
Input for updating an existing time off schedule. Entries are managed via the dedicated time off entry mutations (create_time_off_entry, update_time_off_entry, delete_time_off_entry).
